        <h3 class="card-title">The Digital Financial Revolution</h3>
        <p>Cryptocurrency isn't just another asset class ‚Äì it's a fundamental shift in how we think about money and finance. Bitcoin alone has outperformed every traditional asset over the past decade.</p>

        <div class="insight-box">
          <p>üí° <strong>Key Insight:</strong> Institutional adoption is accelerating. BlackRock, Fidelity, and major banks now offer crypto products. When the world's largest asset managers are buying, that's a signal.</p>
        </div>

        <p>Unlike stocks that trade 6.5 hours a day, crypto markets run 24/7/365. This means you can react to news immediately, trade around your schedule, and never miss an opportunity because markets are closed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="drivers-grid">
