          These are the most traded and liquid cryptocurrencies for active traders.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="crypto-grid">
        {topCryptos.map((crypto) => (
          <div class="crypto-card">
            <div class="crypto-symbol">{crypto.symbol}</div>
            <div class="crypto-info">
              <h4 class="crypto-name">{crypto.name}</h4>
              <p class="crypto-description">{crypto.description}</p>
              <span class="crypto-mcap">Market Cap: {crypto.marketCap}</span>
