        <h3 class="card-title">Bitcoin vs Altcoins: Which Should You Trade?</h3>
        <p><strong>Bitcoin (BTC)</strong> is the safest choice for beginners. It has the highest liquidity, lowest spreads, and most predictable price action. It's also the least likely to go to zero.</p>
        <p><strong>Ethereum (ETH)</strong> is the second-safest option. As the leading smart contract platform, it powers DeFi and NFTs. More volatile than Bitcoin, but with strong fundamentals.</p>
        <p><strong>Altcoins</strong> offer higher potential returns but much higher risk. Many altcoins lose 90%+ in bear markets. Only trade altcoins with money you can afford to lose completely.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BEST BROKERS SECTION -->
  <section class="section" id="brokers">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Best Platforms for Crypto Trading in 2026</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Regulated brokers offering crypto CFDs with competitive spreads and professional tools.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="brokers-grid">
        {featuredBrokers.map((broker) => (
          <div class={`broker-card ${broker.featured ? 'featured' : ''}`}>
            <img src={broker.logo} alt={broker.name} class="broker-logo">
            <div class="broker-rating">
              <span class="rating-score">{broker.rating}</span>
              <span class="rating-stars">{broker.stars}</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="broker-features">
              {broker.features.map((feature) => (
                <li>{feature}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <a href={broker.ctaLink} class="cta-button primary">{broker.ctaText}</a>
            <p class="broker-review-link">
              <a href={broker.reviewLink}>Read full review</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="brokers-tip">
        <p>üí° <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> For long-term holding, use an exchange. For active trading with leverage, use a regulated CFD broker.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STRATEGIES SECTION -->
  <section class="section section-alt" id="strategies">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Crypto Trading Strategies</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          From HODLing to day trading, find the approach that fits your style.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-card">
        <h3 class="card-title">1. HODLing (Buy and Hold)</h3>
        <p>The simplest strategy: buy Bitcoin or Ethereum and hold for months or years. Historically, holding Bitcoin for 4+ years has always been profitable regardless of entry point.</p>
        <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Beginners, long-term investors, people who don't want to watch charts daily.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-card">
        <h3 class="card-title">2. Dollar-Cost Averaging (DCA)</h3>
        <p>Invest a fixed amount at regular intervals (weekly, monthly) regardless of price. This removes emotion and timing risk from the equation.</p>
        <p><strong>Example:</strong> Invest $100 every Monday into Bitcoin. Over time, you'll buy more when prices are low and less when high.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-card">
        <h3 class="card-title">3. Swing Trading</h3>
        <p>Hold positions for days to weeks, capturing medium-term price swings. Use technical analysis to identify trends and reversals.</p>
        <p><strong>Best for:</strong> Traders who can check charts a few times per day but don't want to day trade.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-card">
        <h3 class="card-title">4. Day Trading</h3>
        <p>Open and close positions within the same day. Requires significant time commitment, fast decision-making, and strict risk management.</p>
        <div class="insight-box">
          <p>‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Warning:</strong> Studies show 70-80% of day traders lose money. Master swing trading before attempting to day trade.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RISK WARNING -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="risk-warning">
        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Risk Warning:</strong> Cryptocurrency is highly volatile and speculative. Prices can drop 50%+ in weeks. Never invest more than you can afford to lose. This is not financial advice. CFD trading carries additional risks ‚Äì 68-85% of retail accounts lose money trading CFDs.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQs -->
  <section class="section section-alt" id="faqs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Cryptocurrency Trading FAQs</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-container">
        {faqs.map((faq, index) => (
          <div class="faq-item" id={`faq-${index}`}>
            <button class="faq-question" onclick={`toggleFaq(${index})`}>
              {faq.question}
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <p>{faq.answer}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="section-cta">
        <h3 class="cta-heading">Ready to Start Trading Crypto?</h3>
        <p class="cta-text">
          Join millions of traders in the cryptocurrency market.
        </p>
        <a href="/brokers/avatrade" class="cta-button primary large">
          Start Trading with AvaTrade ‚Üí
        </a>
        <p class="cta-features">
          ‚úì 20+ cryptocurrencies ‚Ä¢ ‚úì Regulated broker ‚Ä¢ ‚úì Free demo account
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RELATED GUIDES -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Related Guides</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="related-grid">
        <a href="/guides/how-to-trade-bitcoin" class="related-card">
          <span class="related-icon">‚Çø</span>
          <h3>How to Trade Bitcoin</h3>
          <p>In-depth guide to trading the world's first cryptocurrency</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/exchanges" class="related-card">
          <span class="related-icon">üè¶</span>
          <h3>Crypto Exchanges</h3>
          <p>Compare the best platforms to buy and sell cryptocurrency</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/guides/forex-trading-basics" class="related-card">
          <span class="related-icon">üí±</span>
          <h3>Forex Trading Basics</h3>
          <p>Learn how forex compares to cryptocurrency trading</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* ==========================================================================
   HERO SECTION
   ========================================================================== */

.hero-section {
  padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f0f23 100%);
  color: var(--white);
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero-section::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 70%, rgba(247, 147, 26, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
              radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(98, 126, 234, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.hero-content {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-xs);
  background: rgba(247, 147, 26, 0.2);
